mighty grim for Azumi.

207
00:08:55,326 --> 00:08:57,536
So who would you rate to
be the main contenders

208
00:08:57,620 --> 00:08:58,250
at this point?

209
00:08:58,371 --> 00:08:59,121
‐ Hey, I’m easy.

210
00:08:59,205 --> 00:09:01,035
So who’s up next?

211
00:09:01,124 --> 00:09:02,254
‐ I lost my needle.

212
00:09:02,375 --> 00:09:04,745
So if anyone finds
it, let me know.

213
00:09:04,878 --> 00:09:06,498
Hold still.

214
00:09:06,588 --> 00:09:08,878
‐ [Man] Wow, Miss Nigumi
can nurse me anytime.

215
00:09:09,007 --> 00:09:09,837
Who’s next?

216
00:09:09,924 --> 00:09:11,304
‐ It’s the Halmay girls.

217
00:09:11,384 --> 00:09:12,844
They do everything together,

218
00:09:12,927 --> 00:09:14,597
but that will make judging
them rather difficult.

219
00:09:14,721 --> 00:09:17,061
‐ It would be shame to break
up such a nicely matched set.

220
00:09:17,182 --> 00:09:19,062
(pop music)

221
00:09:19,142 --> 00:09:20,772
‐ Just look at them.

222
00:09:20,894 --> 00:09:21,944
They’re great.

223
00:09:22,062 --> 00:09:23,562
They’re all so talented.

224
00:09:23,646 --> 00:09:25,856
Could you imagine being a Jovian

225
00:09:25,940 --> 00:09:28,530
and never learning to do
anything well except fight?

226
00:09:33,782 --> 00:09:36,702
‐ And here she is,
ladies and gentlemen,

227
00:09:36,785 --> 00:09:39,955
the star of the evening,
entry number 1578,

228
00:09:40,080 --> 00:09:41,120
Miss Yurika Misumara.

229
00:09:41,247 --> 00:09:42,457
‐ We don’t have 1500 entries.

230
00:09:42,582 --> 00:09:44,832
‐ Such a combination
of beauty and talent

231
00:09:44,918 --> 00:09:46,338
has never been seen before.

232
00:09:46,419 --> 00:09:48,549
The fire maiden of Mars,
the queen of outer space,

233
00:09:48,630 --> 00:09:50,170
